    "It can prevent the private training data from being leaked based on the parameter configurations at a small cost of model utility.",
    "Limiting the accessibility to the model and generating limited prediction results might be another option [312].",
    "Extensive research studies can obtain proper knowledge of to what extent algorithmic defenses such as differential privacy can prevent PII disclosure without compromising model utility.",
